{"tid":1903750,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"杏花邨 黃店 Paradise cafe 求懲罰!!!","createTime":"2020-02-29T07:13:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-10T21:12:25.000Z","uid":319687,"like":88,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"74ddcc5de028dc619e33524c3f3e8e2f32ad2da3","tid":1903750,"uid":319687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T07:13:30.000Z","msg":"琴日去佐 杏花新城入面既黃店 - Paradise cafe 食扒,<br />\n由於疫情關係佢地既生意少佐好多, 每月<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">蝕成20皮以上</span></span></strong>,<br />\n開鋪2年, 蝕足頭一年,<br />\n第2年尾多得大家懲罰先至有少少利潤<br />\n到今年1月尾又殺過愛國肺炎, <span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">生意插水</span></strong></span><br />\n為佐幫補生意, 西餐廳而家做埋外賣生意, <br />\n大家住附近,同時路過杏花邨 可以<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大大力咁懲罰佢地</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">外賣熱線: 2813 5328</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我琴晚食果個餐<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nrLqsJ9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnrLqsJ9.jpg&h=0ed52fa8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢地份Menu, 而家仲有得外賣, 仲有8折<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j8L6cbi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj8L6cbi.jpg&h=247909c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ooJC3hZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FooJC3hZ.jpg&h=9313559a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鋪頭入面仲有旋轉木馬, 影相一流<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XLjCiRK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXLjCiRK.jpg&h=eeb52a55&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n<br />\n過去的參與<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cP6ExdN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcP6ExdN.png&h=5518c217&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/487Hu0t.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F487Hu0t.png&h=dd527f6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UELmLyP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUELmLyP.png&h=08a07ba6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9cd5bd4ea4b6acbf15b51dcc9669fdf0e6f19ebc","tid":1903750,"uid":122720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T07:14:16.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3dc10658e4c3491780544596a8f138b8a5f3fcf2","tid":1903750,"uid":21545,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T07:29:05.000Z","msg":"你準備提早收鋪都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f35e8e62b4dea213f19b1d1ece2e5d1fb038404","tid":1903750,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T07:29:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搬去cc tai 或飲食台 好似適合啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32d85a0abef3a5a642055e03e8ccd8130ee1cabd","tid":1903750,"uid":213163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T07:32:49.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3ed358164f1faece5f8bd6bd6e65bbcffa4e3f30","tid":1903750,"uid":81084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T07:35:41.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"dea861d4b3e2984aaa70c0d9a5928360240fc1f2","tid":1903750,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T07:59:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7560b7474486cba296c5aa1fa4a022fde777354b","tid":1903750,"uid":200663,"like":3,"dislike